{"tid":745450,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[背Notes考試系列] 有冇人記性真係好唔掂？有冇方法解決？","createTime":"2018-07-16T18:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T07:03:19.000Z","uid":85740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"33f4912cf14f1d52d3bd841ce8421c9051d9b1a0","tid":745450,"uid":85740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"明明平時上堂已經好專心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nassignment 都一定係A range<br />\n偏偏midterm 考試出埋奶力都係啱啱過mean<br />\n眼見一班英文唔好 又溫書少過自己嘅同學同自己同grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甚至高grade過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想問下巴絲們有咩方法解決呢個問題，係自己真係無記性呢個功能 定係真係唔識溫書<br />\n<br />\n我溫書係邊讀邊抄，但唔會刻意去背/記，因為覺得好難<br />\n但身邊啲同學真係可以由第一頁背到最後一頁（未必明內容，但係背得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n求記憶大師教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da17b8eea7183543bf3f131e6de61b71e6db5620","tid":745450,"uid":35637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"呢種能力天生的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d人就咁望2下就記實左<br />\nBtw<br />\n有幾個方法幫助記憶<br />\n第一係將要記的野分類好<br />\n例如swimming running係運動<br />\n整理好d野<br />\n第二係將溫書個時身體狀況重現<br />\n例如溫書你會飲咖啡溫<br />\n考試都唔該飲杯咖啡咁考<br />\n第三係減少環境影響<br />\n要聽歌都盡量唔好聽有歌詞的<br />\n<br />\n利申讀9背的科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20ed060aeeebaa6c7214f1c8641c7b3b67a6ca6","tid":745450,"uid":35637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"仲有係咁有規律地複習<br />\n可以將溫左的野變長期記憶<br />\n姐係星期1-5 日日溫一個鐘<br />\n當然要實行好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82b54ed246a52e863c5eb80272432062693a336","tid":745450,"uid":50162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"明白理解消化過後就易入腦好多"},{"pid":"fb38b0875d1fb2affcbb2067c38edefd95da29e1","tid":745450,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:51:17.000Z","msg":"抄讀背係最強<br />\n<br />\n但只係短期記憶<br />\n<br />\n信不信由你"},{"pid":"aa6845023598465298b29f96dcec81d62958e693","tid":745450,"uid":85740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da17b8eea7183543bf3f131e6de61b71e6db5620","tid":745450,"uid":35637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"呢種能力天生的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d人就咁望2下就記實左<br />\nBtw<br />\n有幾個方法幫助記憶<br />\n第一係將要記的野分類好<br />\n例如swimming running係運動<br />\n整理好d野<br />\n第二係將溫書個時身體狀況重現<br />\n例如溫書你會飲咖啡溫<br />\n考試都唔該飲杯咖啡咁考<br />\n第三係減少環境影響<br />\n要聽歌都盡量唔好聽有歌詞的<br />\n<br />\n利申讀9背的科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪有讀過psycho嘅course <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲concept有啲熟"},{"pid":"a2798dee5a7304e6bade1113ac349278d548287f","tid":745450,"uid":134907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"唔溫<br />\n臨考個晚知死<br />\n死都溫哂佢 <br />\n最後a range<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d12ab6880b150e0c3e0fd096e349b35c007ce2","tid":745450,"uid":85740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:55:25.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係細佬讀文科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論啲人點樣識都好 去到考試一樣要靠背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲老師好撚鍾意問definition <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者問concept comparison <br />\n<br />\n我次次最好表現就係mc同lq（因為活學活用啲，通常都係比case代入）"},{"pid":"2fc504da7b613491ee056b06c348a9318edbcddf","tid":745450,"uid":85740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2798dee5a7304e6bade1113ac349278d548287f","tid":745450,"uid":134907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"唔溫<br />\n臨考個晚知死<br />\n死都溫哂佢 <br />\n最後a range<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得㗎 我提早3-4日溫都係啱啱好時間咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨考溫如同自殺"},{"pid":"1732ec2c192120aadb2e3b5e4ce43de58974fb5f","tid":745450,"uid":140678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T19:15:02.000Z","msg":"將啲concept用自己語言/文字記落黎 <br />\n用好短既key words 然後背左佢 <br />\n<br />\n例如鳩嗡當講機會成本 ，就係你想打丁又想溫書，但你揀左打丁，咁放棄溫書就係你既機會成本<br />\n<br />\n咁下次你諗起打丁或者用呢兩個字 就會諗到機會成本個概念<br />\n<br />\n自己用自己既文字/語言/符號會特別深刻記憶"},{"pid":"3e10aee1c678cea3490b86ab60952e7d93ad9a50","tid":745450,"uid":140678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T19:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將啲concept用自己語言/文字記落黎 <br />\n用好短既key words 然後背左佢 <br />\n<br />\n例如鳩嗡當講機會成本 ，就係你想打丁又想溫書，但你揀左打丁，咁放棄溫書就係你既機會成本<br />\n<br />\n咁下次你諗起打丁或者用呢兩個字 就會諗到機會成本個概念<br />\n<br />\n自己用自己既文字/語言/符號會特別深刻記憶</blockquote><br />\n之後你邊抄邊背就可以每個concept 只抄返幾粒字，一路用幾粒字背返啲野出來，你會發覺背幾粒字就會背到哂啲野"},{"pid":"61b2b38009ea5c9921495e31db5b02acd5934ef3","tid":745450,"uid":33568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T19:19:45.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n我既嚴重程度係可以唔記得最熟幾個同學既全名<br />\n讀中文<br />\n放棄左背書好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAssignment 證明實力"},{"pid":"7eb837508c5f9edc83384bc380e65713d09ec5ef","tid":745450,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"